{"tid":1517145,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【校園欺凌】學校已有既定機制（訓導主任）處理","createTime":"2019-08-30T00:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:51:52.000Z","uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f85ca38165b782eae17cd9674b609d61038e886c","tid":1517145,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T00:04:59.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄︰教育局嚴厲譴責校園欺凌行為<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府召開跨部門記者會關注校園欺凌情況。教育局批評有人散播仇恨情緒，予以嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，教育及保護學生是教育人員的天職，若有人被確認參與欺凌行為，學校會採取紀律行動，教育局必定會作出懲處，包括考慮涉事人員是否適合繼續擔任教職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360932&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360932%26refer%3D&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8lmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=e0b3624c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360932%26refer%3D&h=93eb2c38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=360932&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔重申，學校已有既定機制（訓導主任）處理，無需教育局介入</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89583071974d12e6314cce30dfbf3bc7fef83da1","tid":1517145,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:51:52.000Z","msg":"香港獨立之後應該搵邊首歌做國歌？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dHtRqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dHtRqS</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#73樓 UserID#140326 葡萄乘淑儀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我都係獨立派<br />\n你做乜屈我熱？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>解釋！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一日唔道歉，你個個 post 都會見到我</span></span>"}]}